"<name>`` statements now include suggestions for the value of ``<name>`` "
"based on the available names in ``<module>``. (Contributed by Pablo Galindo "
"in :gh:`91058`.)"
msgstr ""
"Le eccezioni :exc:`ImportError` sollevate da dichiarazioni di ``from "
