#: whatsnew/3.12.rst:2140
msgid ""
"Argument parsing functions like :c:func:`PyArg_ParseTuple` doesn't support "
"``Py_UNICODE*`` based format (e.g. ``u``, ``Z``) anymore. Please migrate to "
